Phil Weinzimer is president of Strategere Consulting and works with clients to develop business and IT strategies that focus on achieving business outcomes. He has written two books, the most recent, The Strategic CIO: Changing the Dynamics of the Business Enterprise. , focuses on how strategic CIOs leverage information and technolog for competitive advantage. Additionally, he writes articles on strategic IT, including one for CIO Magazine, co-authored a Harvard Case Study, conducts video interview series for Sarder TV-IT Strategtic Thought Leaders-and for Accelerating IT Success-The Strategic CIO: Managing in the 21st Century, as well as speaks at CIO events on IT Strategy and How Strategic CIOs are Changing the Dynamics of the Business Enterprise


