            Filippo Passerini on the IT Organization of the Future
        



The Chief Information Officer of Procter & Gamble Talks to Craig Lawton, a Senior Partner at The Boston Consulting Group






            February 17, 2009
        

            
            by
            
            
Craig  Lawton






            Categories:


                Technology & Digital, 
            
            
                Consumer & Retail













